'''ITO-9''' was an [[Interrogation droid/Legends|interrogation droid]] abandoned when its [[Starship/Legends|starship]] was destroyed in space. It was commonly known as a [[Void Droid]] that patrolled the [[Paradise system/Legends|Paradise system]] junkyards. It was equipped with a [[laser scalpel]], [[power shears]], a [[Hypodermic injector/Legends|hypodermic injector]], and a [[Grenade/Legends|grenade]].

